channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Protests against Israel's war in Gaza rattle colleges across the US
item.description: Colleges and universities held graduation ceremonies this weekend as pro-Palestinian protests continued on campuses across the US. Follow for live updates.

item.title: Trump trial live updates: Testimony suggests Trump signed Cohen checks in White House
item.description: Follow the latest developments in former President Donald Trump's criminal hush money trial in New York.

item.title: Former Trump Org. executive testifies in hush money trial
item.description: Former President Donald Trump's hush money trial continues in New York. Follow here for the latest live news updates, analysis and more.

item.title: 'Miracle': Pastor credits divine intervention after man pulls gun on him in church
item.description: A church service in Pennsylvania came to a terrifying halt on Sunday when authorities say a man pulled a gun on the pastor.

item.title: Significant tornado outbreak possible in Central US
item.description: Strong, long-lived tornadoes are possible in Oklahoma and Kansas on Monday as ingredients come together for a significant severe storm outbreak.

item.title: Abducted 10-month-old girl has been found, officials say
item.description: Police issued an Amber Alert for 10-month-old Eleia Maria Torres, which was active Saturday morning.

item.title: The beautiful Croatia coastline with fewer tourists
item.description: Mention Dalmatia, and Split and Dubrovnik usually spring to mind. But head to the northern stretch of this coastal Croatian region and you'll find a road a little less traveled.

item.title: Russia announces nuclear weapon drills after angry exchange with Western officials
item.description: Russia is threatening to strike British military facilities and says it plans to hold drills simulating the use of battlefield nuclear weapons

item.title: Israel tells Gazans in parts of eastern Rafah to evacuate
item.description: Israel's military has told people in eastern Rafah to "evacuate immediately," Follow for live updates.

item.title: Robinhood receives SEC notice for alleged securities violations at crypto unit
item.description: Robinhood Markets Inc. has received a notice from the Securities and Exchange Commission about alleged securities violations at its crypto division
